title: Do I invest in growth or infrastructure first? Reid Hoffman & Kickstarter's Everette Taylor weigh in
description:
How do you balance chasing growth with building the systems to support it? In our latest Strategy Session, Masters of Scale host Reid Hoffman and Kickstarter CEO Everette Taylor tackle a classic founder dilemma: when to double down on traction and when to invest in scalable operations.
